00:39:49,554 --> 00:39:51,972
I'd really rather watch it alone.

390
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:54,600
Really.

391
00:39:55,518 --> 00:39:56,769
Whatever.

392
00:40:12,035 --> 00:40:19,208
Come on.

