411
00:45:29,977 --> 00:45:31,603
All right. Well, I'll keep that in mind.

412
00:45:32,688 --> 00:45:34,898
- Have a nice day.
- You, too.

413
00:46:23,865 --> 00:46:25,740
- Hi.
- Sorry I'm late.

