00:46:49,265 --> 00:46:51,516
Well, here you go.

421
00:46:52,059 --> 00:46:53,351
- Thanks.
- Sure.

422
00:47:25,676 --> 00:47:26,676
Hey, Ruthie, it's me.

423
00:47:27,136 --> 00:47:29,471
