447
00:51:06,021 --> 00:51:07,355
Our son.

448
00:51:32,673 --> 00:51:34,340
You take my picture.

449
00:51:38,721 --> 00:51:40,180
I've seen you.

450
00:51:41,348 --> 00:51:43,683
When I'm in the yard at school.

451
00:51:44,894 --> 00:51:46,394
You're there.

452
00:51:48,731 --> 00:51:50,398
