477
00:54:08,662 --> 00:54:10,496
What happened to her?

478
00:54:11,081 --> 00:54:12,415
I don't know yet.

479
00:54:12,499 --> 00:54:15,668
But I think it has something to do
with the horses.

480
00:54:16,003 --> 00:54:17,587
I think we should go
to the island together.

